# A complete setup file for a system with the Stillinger-Weber potential
# 2013/10/21 Henrik Andersen Sveinsson


units real
atom_style atomic
newton on # Required by sw
boundary p p p

pair_style sw

read_data data.stillingerwebertest

replicate 4 4 4


pair_coeff * * Si.sw Si


thermo_style multi

dump 1 all xyz 100 sw_non_periodic2.xyz

minimize 1.0e-6 1.0e-8 100 1000

fix 1 all nvt temp 100.0 10.0 10.0

run 200000